tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE datasets (
    dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name TEXT,
    dataset_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE models (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    dataset_id INT,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES datasets(id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    experiment_description TEXT,
    model_id INT,
    dataset_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE models (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    version VARCHAR(50),
    status VARCHAR(50),
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE metadata (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    experiment_id INT,
    key VARCHAR(100),
    value TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
